Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Signed-off-by: Stefan Berger <stefanb@linux.ibm.com>
Reviewed-by: Marc-Andr√© Lureau <marcandre.lureau@redhat.com>
